A label node specifies the reference number and a placement.

@<parsing rules@>=
placement: TOP {$$=LABEL_TOP;} |  BOT {$$=LABEL_BOT;} |  MID {$$=LABEL_MID;} | {$$=LABEL_MID;};
content_node: START LABEL REFERENCE placement END @|
              {  hset_label($3,$4); @+};
