  memmove(hpos,t->t,t->s);
  hpos=hpos+t->s;
  free(t->t);
@

We output all outline definitions from 0 to |max_outline| and
check that every one of them has a title. Thereby we make sure
that in the short format |max_outline| matches the number of 
outline definitions.

